OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joan
OL,4,CJohnson
OL,6,FJoan Johnson, Age 98, Auxiliary
OL,7,FTerritorial Service
OL,9,FInterviewed 17 November 2023
OL,11,FJoining the Women's Land Army at the
OL,12,Fage of 18 Joan Johnson later
OL,13,Ftransferred to the ATS and became a
OL,14,Fdriver.
OL,16,FShe had trained at the same base as
OL,17,FQueen Elizabeth where she learned to
OL,18,Fdrive vehicles including Dodge trucks
OL,19,Fand Bedford three-ton trucks as well
OL,20,Fas motorbikes.
