OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joan
OL,4,CJohnson
OL,6,FWomen in the ATS did an essential job
OL,7,Fas drivers and mechanics and were
OL,8,Fpressed into action in the long months
OL,9,Fleading up to the invasion.
OL,11,F"The exact locations to drop the
OL,12,Florries were kept secret from her at a
OL,13,Ftime when much of the South coast was
OL,14,Fcut off from the general public - and
OL,15,Fwhen the Allies were slowly building
OL,16,Fup caches of vehicles and supplies.
OL,18,F"There were no signposts," she said.
