OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joan
OL,4,CJohnson
OL,6,F"Nobody knew where we were going. We
OL,7,Fhad a dispatch rider to take us so we
OL,8,Fdidn't know where we were. We just
OL,9,Fknew we were near the coast."
OL,11,FShe remembers parking the vehicles in
OL,12,Fremote and often wooded sites where
OL,13,Fthey were then camouflaged. Before
OL,14,Fbeing driven back to base ahead of a
OL,15,Frepeat journey the next day.
OL,17,F"I was so pleased after it was all
OL,18,Fover," she said.
OL,20,F"And then I had to think about what I
OL,21,Fwould do with my life."
